BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Open URL / Open URL With Selection

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString:
set cbjson to do shell script "curl -H 'CB-VERSION: 2015-04-08' https://api.coinbase.com/v2/prices/ETH-USD/spot"set cbjson to do shell script "sed s/warnings.*//g <<< " & cbjsonset ethprice to do shell script "sed s/[a-zA-Z:{},]//g <<< " & cbjsonset tauprice to do shell script "curl -s -d '{\"operationName\": \"tokens\",\"variables\": {},\"query\": \"fragment TokenFields on Token {derivedETH} query tokens { tokens(where: {id: \\\"0xc27a2f05fa577a83ba0fdb4c38443c0718356501\\\"}) {...TokenFields  __typename }  pairs0: pairs(where: {token1: \\\"0xc27a2f05fa577a83ba0fdb4c38443c0718356501\\\"}, first: 50, orderBy: reserveUSD, orderDirection: desc) { id     __typename }}\"}' -X POST https://api.thegraph.com/subgraphs/name/uniswap/uniswap-v2 | sed -E 's/.*derivedETH\":\"([0-9\\.]+).*/\\1/'"set usdprice to ethprice * tauprice
set truncatedResult to do shell script "echo '"&  usdprice &"' | awk '{ for (i=1; i<=NF; ++i) $i=sprintf(\"%.6s\", $i); print }'"return "$" & truncatedResult
